{"id":274814,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-数百名参加襄渝铁路建设的三线学兵连成/","date":"2013-01-16T13:01:20Z","modified":"2013-01-16T13:01:20Z","title":"维权网 | 数百名参加襄渝铁路建设的三线学兵连成员到陕西省政府请愿维权(图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日下午</span><span>，数百名参加过当年襄渝铁路建设的三线学兵连成员到陕西省政府东门请愿。他们打出了：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>省信访局已经沦为截访局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的横幅表达不满。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当年去参加建设襄渝铁路时，三线学兵连学员都只有十六七岁，而修路工作危险繁重，曾经导致多人死亡和伤残。现在学员们要求维权补偿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>此前陕西三线学兵连成员曾多次大规模到陕西省政府门前表达维权诉求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/11/blog-post_9663.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/11/blog-post_9663.html</a></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-czHyw-PskXU/UPZqmQ8592I/AAAAAAAAZB8/OD77aA3ptWM/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"290\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-czHyw-PskXU/UPZqmQ8592I/AAAAAAAAZB8/OD77aA3ptWM/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4mbZTerE0BU/UPZqnjwG3GI/AAAAAAAAZCE/yTITV17PUSM/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"235\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4mbZTerE0BU/UPZqnjwG3GI/AAAAAAAAZCE/yTITV17PUSM/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IhK7jdZdkCM/UPZqooornxI/AAAAAAAAZCM/DRKp4b_76zM/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"237\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IhK7jdZdkCM/UPZqooornxI/AAAAAAAAZCM/DRKp4b_76zM/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<di